{
  "texts": [
    "With the growing number of training episodes, the exploration rate should be continuously reduced to achieve rapid convergence of the model.",
    "Therefore, the value of ϵ decreases by Δϵ in each episode.",
    "The initial ϵ value ϵ 0 is set to 0.9, with an ϵ decrement of Δϵ CW = 1 × 10 -3 in cliff walking (CW) and Δϵ MS = 5 × 10 -6 in material synthesis (MS).",
    "Nature Communications | (2024) 15:1044"
  ]
}